title: #92Noon! 11a Hour 5/13 - Micheletti/Garofalo
description: Charch continues his trek through the 2022 Vikings Schedule, welcomes in Pat Micheletti to his thoughts on the end of the Wild season, and Pat Garofalo calls in to talk about the latest on sports wagering legalization in Minnesota!
